{"tid":2243080,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"女主播「裸體圍裙」報財經新聞？網友全歪樓　走出攝影棚真相大白","createTime":"2020-10-14T13:02:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T14:02:54.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"eaf7e00e4b69364c0f93a95975c7a738c2c1236f","tid":2243080,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:02:32.000Z","msg":"日本正妹女主播井口綾子外型甜美，同時擁有脫俗氣質，近來站上主播台播報財經新聞時，穿搭卻意外呈現出「裸體圍裙」的視覺感，令日本網友乍看之下誤以為沒穿衣服。對此，電視台官方推特日前曬出一系列幕後照片，才讓真相大白。<br />\n<br />\n新聞截圖中，井口綾子穿著膚色無袖荷葉邊吊帶衣，加上鏡頭前一度截掉下半身畫面，一度讓部分網友歪樓、誤以為是穿著裸體圍裙播報，「還以為裡面沒穿」、「不會太性感了嗎」。<br />\n<br />\n然而，電視台TBS事後於官方推特上發文，公開井口綾子在後台穿著同件衣服的全身自拍照，直接證明了該件衣服是吊帶褲、並非圍裙，且是由長期合作的服飾品牌所提供，意外在日網掀起不小討論度。"},{"pid":"ca6aaa82f0390a8ef6248879de573c56a333565d","tid":2243080,"uid":261849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:03:08.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">圖呢</span>"},{"pid":"7a8b7444248e671e4310fbf9e769c005a07fe160","tid":2243080,"uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:03:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5202/d5202375.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5202%2Fd5202375.jpg&h=a8677674&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲井口綾子播報被誤以為穿「裸體圍裙」。（圖／翻攝自livedoor）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5202/d5202373.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5202%2Fd5202373.jpg&h=6e087ff3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5202/d5202372.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5202%2Fd5202372.jpg&h=a2a27f6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5202/d5202371.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5202%2Fd5202371.jpg&h=2c2d788e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5202/d5202370.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5202%2Fd5202370.jpg&h=e0877810&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲電視台曬出井口綾子幕後自拍照。（圖／翻攝自TBS官方推特）"},{"pid":"16b5c586aed5074ed90ae7c9e3dc4a091e5fa5a2","tid":2243080,"uid":261849,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:04:03.000Z","msg":"肉地架妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4723d28ca80c6e089646875b2e2d5f2008769363","tid":2243080,"uid":320204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca6aaa82f0390a8ef6248879de573c56a333565d","tid":2243080,"uid":261849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:03:08.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">圖呢</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:04:44.000Z","msg":"你慢少少我就可以名正言順po依個gif了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NFoPYaR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNFoPYaR.gif&h=90443b14&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d953ba48bfe5af7dbf1f829f5035d6b93229759","tid":2243080,"uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"16b5c586aed5074ed90ae7c9e3dc4a091e5fa5a2","tid":2243080,"uid":261849,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:04:03.000Z","msg":"肉地架妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:05:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.ctwant.com/images/content/5/78305/0cf437eb33ee7166cf12b476aefe9fd4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ctwant.com%2Fimages%2Fcontent%2F5%2F78305%2F0cf437eb33ee7166cf12b476aefe9fd4.jpg&h=1714f0bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20cc94ecdb93524fcf39cda3cd46273bf14861a7","tid":2243080,"uid":135977,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"16b5c586aed5074ed90ae7c9e3dc4a091e5